data.description: A home on 1 acre of land to do so many things on, surrounded by apple, pear, plumb, & peach trees, abundance of nature & river views! No need to pack up your kayak, just jump right in to cruise Duck Creek that will bring you to the bay. Prepare your meals w/ your own fresh herbs: rosemary, white sage, peppermint, spearmint, lavender. Relax outside on the deck, or the firepit or head inside to get cozy! Unique character flows throughout w/ granite countertops, brick, walk-in closet from the bathroom, natural light from many rooms, 1st floor laundry, a pull up door leading to the basement w/ newer furnace, A/C & water heater. Laundry can be relocated to basement to utilize 1st FL room differently. Heated garage, privacy fence. Home has been appraised at a higher value then asking price.
